{"url": "https://people.com/food/applebees-dollar-strawberry-margaritas-august-details/", "text": "If you\u2019re looking for a way to cool down this summer without breaking the bank, Applebee\u2019s has got your back.\n\nFor the entire month of August, the restaurant chain is offering strawberry margaritas (or as they call them \u201cDollaritas\u201d) for only $1. The beverage is made with tequila, strawberry and margarita mix and is served in a cold 10-ounce mug.\n\nApplebee\u2019s is known to give customers a good deal\u2014they previously offered $1 Long Island Iced Teas last December, and most recently kicked off the spring season with their signature margaritas for only a buck. They also announced the return of their \u201call-you-can-eat\u201d menu in January and added $1 Bahama Mamas to their menu in February.\n\nRELATED VIDEO: How to Make Watermelon Margaritas\n\n\u201cIt\u2019s crazy to think that our most popular drink could get any better, but with the addition of strawberry, our guests are going to love how good this Dollarita tastes,\u201d says Patrick Kirk, the vice president of beverage innovation at Applebee\u2019s. \u201cThe Strawberry Dollarita is the perfect way to cool down on those hot August days and enjoy the final days of summer.\u201d", "images": ["https://people.com/thmb/xM9tkaBxqgMYFlup1dr_gBISXOc=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(999x0:1001x2)/starbucks-102523-7f9b2dd8089c4b2ca5eef67f41dfa68b.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/Lje7sGaj3HgeS-yLg9z5JSNPfrU=/300x150/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/people_magazine_sub-e6689738996d40f38f154099e1751481.png", "https://people.com/thmb/7sfnu0w4Wli7Kxd-BNj60-pcwO0=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(748x123:750x125)/wendys-jr-bacon-cheeseburger-091223-1-032bf1c0cb1446a1a42175df080553ff.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/w4_QD_ibhoOLiIbOqFW4I2E-yCc=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(699x502:701x5